title: Mid Season Invitational?
body: Yo! anyone going from Orlando Fri-Sun?  Was hoping to maybe find someone to share ride/motel? with.  Sorry if this isn't the right place to post this but strangers you're mah only hope!

replies.body:
Winter Springs here. Renting a van with some friends so we can ride in comfort.

Already have hotel reservations as well.
Add me in game, we can chat there.
Sent~ gotta get rdy for work now though.  hopefully I'll catch you later or tomorrow :)

Good luck on finding a ride/splitises.

I'll be driving from the West Coast, and staying with Relatives. /lucky
Hours? I'm off the next couple of days. I'm generally up pretty early since I normally work early morning shifts.
